lead_paragraph: Limited overs specialist Jos Buttler will replace the struggling Ben Duckett in a rejigged England batting lineup, skipper Alastair Cook confirmed ahead of his team's third test against India beginning on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Buttler Replaces Duckett in England's Rejigged Order
